      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Draft Ring-fenced Bodies (Amendment) (EU Exit) Regulations 2018
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    This publication sets out the proposed amendments to UK legislation related to the UK’s ring-fencing regime, to be laid under the EU (Withdrawal) Act.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
